title: Mike Breen and Jerry Ferrara on the Knicks and Kevin Negandhi on 76ers
description:
Mike Breen and Jerry Ferrara join The Woj Pod to discuss the renaissance of the Knicks and Madison Square Garden in these NBA Playoffs, including why Jerry didn’t name his new son Julius. Also: ESPN’s Kevin Negandhi on his hometown 76ers.
